channel.title: Chosen Pkz 377
channel.description:
Hey guys, i'm not really involved with RSPS's anymore so i thought i would release my Server. The server is a delta base, with a lot of added features.
If you use this i want credit, i dont want leechers. enjoy!
Server Features -iPanel -Walking Npc's -3 different Anti Crasher System's. -Snow in Certain Areas (Can easily Be removed). -Perfect Player Vs Monster Combat. -All 21 Skills working perfect. -13 Quest's With correct requirments like RS. -100's of training areas, many Npc's very Stable no Lag! -Correct Npc drops. -All alters 100% working. -99% ladders & doors working. -Ancient, Lunar, Modern Magics. -New teleport emotes -Just added Runecraft tele Tabs, and normal TeleTabs.
Minigames -Duel arena -63 Jad waves Working Healers. -Warriors guild, drops Defenders. (with working warriors guild interface). -Tormented demond - Drops Dragon Claws. -Barrows -Pest Control -All Godwars Bosses with correct drops.
Emote & More -Working vengeance & Vengeance other. -Working Crossbow emotes (Hits higher Realistic like rs). -All GS special attacks, walk, running, blocking, Emotes. -Defender Block emote. -474 whip emote (not gay like rs, just holds it correctly). -Saradomin Sword Special attack. -All pvp armours & all Correct Spirit Shields. -Dragon Claws special attack. -All dragon weapons have realistic special attacks. -Added Ogre Bows etc like RS. -100% working Chinchompas! with correct emotes and Perfect Hits! -Dragon Bolts -Dark Bow with special attack, not overpowerd. -100% working Dh effect, with correct emotes. -All Barrow armours with correct effects. -And much More!
Player Killing -100% range & mage following. -Correct Spell delays. -Multi Barrage in Multi Zones. -Consitant special attacks like RS. Becuase DDS normally failed on Delta Bases. -Correct wildy Levels, with perfect steps. -Many Pking Areas, Edgvile, Castle, Mage Bank, etc..
